### Event Streaming API Tests
### Tests for EventStreamingController endpoints
### Uses {{baseUrl}} from http-client.env.json
### Note: These endpoints use Server-Sent Events (SSE)

### Subscribe to session events (SSE — connection stays open)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/events/
Accept: text/event-stream
Cache-Control: no-cache
Connection: keep-alive

> {%
  client.log("SSE subscription initiated");
%}

### Subscribe to global events (SSE — connection stays open)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/events/global
Accept: text/event-stream
Cache-Control: no-cache
Connection: keep-alive

> {%
  client.log("Global SSE subscription initiated");
%}
